e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少少手震</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔係好睇得出自己手震，都係人哋話我聽先知<br />\n不過真係少少都要根治左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲麻煩過濕疹，濕疹我戒口已經好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5446807b766d62c1fc568dd537083de86f17602","tid":282421,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎杯水 都手震<br />\n茶樓 勘茶 俾人笑唔夠力</blockquote><br />\n搞搞下真係斟親野比人都驚比佢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4e521cbf5b78f920780a59b0af84c0a783c6c6","tid":282421,"uid":67482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"我都有 但我係高中先開始有<br />\n唔係震得好勁果隻 用力hold住就會震<br />\n睇過醫生 佢話正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話我可能係長期做運動搞到咁"},{"pid":"fd160b5a36257287aefa04b4b354f490d7ccaa17","tid":282421,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落似甲亢 去驗下血就清楚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇左睇，好似冇得斷尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會復發</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係盡快去驗下血⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b3b32c5bf128c2c6367b50c9f0ee5301186ac3c1","tid":282421,"uid":11935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"屌我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔係勁"},{"pid":"8f9f6e2f3451048ddfbcbf7f0f0c73c741a18aa9","tid":282421,"uid":87757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu