img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日比人以為唔夠力/驚<br />\n<br />\n細個打完交隻手震到柏金遜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打完交用力過度，手震應該都屬於正常？"},{"pid":"c05999f61e20acfbc6a4609d1103f6181b0204e4","tid":282421,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落似甲亢 去驗下血就清楚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇左睇，好似冇得斷尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會復發</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係盡快去驗下血⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n驗血好快姐 係醫先長時間</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪就咁係普通科門診睇叫佢轉介驗血就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d563819af30d8c10327fc92fd4bc9e2aeada551","tid":282421,"uid":53823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係<br />\n應該係遺傳既<br />\n我阿媽同有D親戚都係咁<br />\n隻手一要hold 住一個動作就會震<br />\n以前因為咁搞到好冇自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a45657c1d05bdeaf5c6df7bc0326cf39a3512f","tid":282421,"uid":87757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落似甲亢 去驗下血就清楚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇左睇，好似冇得斷尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會復發</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係盡快去驗下血⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n驗血好快姐 係醫先長時間</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪就咁係普通科門診睇叫佢轉介驗血就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前大學clinic睇 不過你去普通門診話自己可能有甲亢 佢應該會叫你驗血 係個門診到應該有埋"},{"pid":"d79c3c5e3ff0d3e7f31902824191c86e6d8bc0fa","tid":282421,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"之前返工就係因為咁而俾女同事恥笑 樣野真係唔係重 而自己都唔覺重<br />\n樣野愈輕就愈手震震咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 我捐過血 如果有事既話 血十字應該通知左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"0319958adb266f0e4f1e738d8424a23a3187aa26","tid":282421,"uid":108685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"男仔有咁既情況真係好撚傷自尊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcecb9441fe3b91250b0d5bdbe3bd5e18ab7571","tid":282421,"uid":87757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前返工就係因為咁而俾女同事恥笑 樣野真係唔係重 而自己都唔覺重<br />\n樣野愈輕就愈手震震咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 我捐過血 如果有事既話 血十字應該通知左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n紅十字應該唔會同你驗甲狀腺素"},{"pid":"c6d952ee5edf2cacc0aadba71bcd3dc50175ca00","tid":282421,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次見工個老細仲直接問我係咪好緊張<br />\n明明個氣氛幾輕鬆冇乜壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45254e2eefde41a6f2fdc7d51504f816eb0e486d","tid":282421,"uid":122751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我天生就手震，唔係因為緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人唔係冇力，拎到重野，但用力個下就係會震，尤其拎外賣個啲好輕既膠匙會震個不停<br />\n成日比朋友笑，工作上都好大影響，成日比人誤會我唔夠力，緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n體重正常（細個係試過過輕，不過宜家BMI 都有19<br />\n有做開帶氧運動 (一星期至少2次, 每次 &gt;= 1hr)<br />\n睇過中醫，有做過針灸，食中藥，但冇乜改善<br />\n<br />\n上網睇到D人話可能係甲狀腺有問題，唔通要去睇西醫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗，分享下解決方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中五開始發現左依個問題, 血都驗過,神經專科都睇過,話可能係原創性手震essential tremor, 自己都上網搵過好多資料, 知道係遺傳(我老豆有) ,無發病原因,暫時無cure,<br />\n。<br />\n有得做手術但有風險唔嚴重都建議食藥,得幾隻藥物舒緩 但有副作用 ,會頭暈, 好似係降低心跳頻率個類。 ps. 研究話酒精會幫助短暫舒緩到,咖啡因會加劇手震。<br />\n<br />\n以前成日俾手震搞到好無自信, d人成日問我係咪好緊張, 拎好輕嘅野都會好震。但依家睇化左。"},{"pid":"111d087b448a61143c873596b7049b70bdfb23aa","tid":282421,"uid":53368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"全身都震，剪頭髮想hold住個頭唔郁就會震"},{"pid":"582314213844c0a0c5dd835792a7d2687258da25","tid":282421,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身都震，剪頭髮想hold住個頭唔郁就會震</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同條女扑野條女未爽到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e12f5d2b95d98add590dbf2684c4d604d7d2051","tid":282421,"uid":13029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身都震，剪頭髮想hold住個頭唔郁就會震</blockquote><br />\n我剪頭髮都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩病黎？"},{"pid":"2612378fd3eed00a9a76b57ee2a1a981f72b156f","tid":282421,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"我有個fd 男仔都有 佢話細個跌親隻手所以當佢一用力就震<br />\n<br />\n有冇check 下手D神經？"},{"pid":"07587186d2b4531a5690a7ded04c70319c48cc8c","tid":282421,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"我打完